        ------------------------------
        Backwards-incompatible changes
        ------------------------------
        
        v0.7
        ====
        
        * ``django_cms_tools.fixtures`` renamed to: ``django_cms_tools.fixture_helper``
        
        * remove ``django_cms_tools.fixtures.languages``
        
